\int_0^{\infty} dk \, K_0\left(\sqrt{a (k^2+b)}\right) = \int_0^{\infty} dt \, \int_0^{\infty} dk \, e^{-\sqrt{a} \cosh{t} \sqrt{k^2+b}}
